# Catch the old Cloudflare slug redirect that browsers cached
/fuel-ix-copilots        /   301!
/fuel-ix-copilots/*      /   301!

# Force HTTP -> HTTPS (covers users cached to http)
http://ai-explained.design/*       https://ai-explained.design/:splat     301!
http://www.ai-explained.design/*   https://www.ai-explained.design/:splat     301!

# Force www -> apex (normalize to non-www)
https://www.ai-explained.design/*  https://ai-explained.design/:splat     301!
